# Shader node checklist

New or changed **`src/shaders/nodes/**`** specs:

1. **`NodeSpec`** — match peers (id, name, category, ports, glsl, …); see `src/types/nodeSpec.ts`.
2. **`node-documentation.json`** — key **`"node:<id>"`** (e.g. `"node:noise"`): title, category, icon, tagline, description, inputs/outputs with `suggestedTargets`, `relatedItems` as needed.
3. **`index.ts`** — export/register the node with the bundle.
4. **`npm run build`** — green types.
5. Align with **`docs/user-goals/04-nodes-and-parameters.md`** if behavior is user-visible.

**Refs:** Existing nodes in `src/shaders/nodes/`, `src/data/node-documentation.json`.
